Class LDLinkedList<T>

java.lang.Object
java.util.AbstractCollection<E>
java.util.AbstractList<T>
LDLinkedList<T>
Type Parameters:
T - The type of elements in this list.
All Implemented Interfaces:
Iterable<T>, Collection<T>, Deque<T>, List<T>, Queue<T>
public class LDLinkedList<T> extends AbstractList<T> implements Deque<T>
A lazily deleted linked list implementation of the List interface. I didn't use List super interface because it isn't necessary.
